  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK440">
<l>kātala kāta laṟiyāmai yuykkiṟpiṉ</l>
<l>ētila vētilār nūl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (a king) enjoys, privately the things which he desires, the designs of his enemies will be useless.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
